geo:siteIdentification.geo:notes: The concrete survey pillar is anchored on the roof on the building of the TBSM Tibet Autonomus Regional Bureau of Surveying and Mapping. The top of the pillar is 12.4 m above the ground. Also an AOA SNR-8000 ACT, Four character ID LHAS, on pillar LS 12, DOMES No. 21613M001 was observing from 1995-02-02 until 2007-01-30.
